data.description: Custom built 4bd 4bath home on 2.98 acres!  One of the most exclusive homes in the neighborhood!  High ceilings,  open floor plan,  bonus room upstairs,  pre-wired for surround system,  huge garage has its own designated A/C unit!  This is truly a unique home that has all the appeals of country living within minutes of 1604 / 151 area.   No restrictions or HOA !!
